title: Wimbledon crowd boo Belarusian player after losing to Ukrainian
description: Belarusian tennis player Victoria Azarenka was booed off Court One at Wimbledon after losing to Ukraine's Elina Svitolina.

title: France bans fireworks sales ahead of Bastille Day after violent riots
description: France has banned the sale of fireworks ahead of Bastille Day celebrations on Friday amid fears of further violence.

title: NATO head 'absolutely' confident allies will agree on formal wording about Ukraine's membership
description: The head of NATO has said he is "absolutely" confident that allies will agree on a form of wording at a summit this week about Ukraine's future accession to the alliance that will be acceptable to Kyiv.

title: Sunak and Biden to meet in UK amid divisions over US plan to send cluster bombs to Ukraine
description: US President Joe Biden will fly to the UK today amid tensions over his decision to send cluster bombs to Ukraine.
